  {{nickName}}

<script>
import { ref } from '@vue/reactivity';
import { useRoute } from 'vue-router'
export default {
  name: 'MyPage',
  setup() {
    const route = useRoute();
    let nickName = ref('');
    nickName.value = route.query.nickName;


    return {nickName};
  }
}
